title: Beautiful Auburn 5bd 3 bath Rental Home
posting_body: ['30107 129th Pl SE, Auburn, WA, 98092', '5 Bed - 3 Bath                    $3,450.00/moSq Footage: 2,590                 $3,450.00/depYear built: 2006', 'Array', 'Beautiful and spacious 5 bedroom, 3 bathroom Norris home in desirable Vintage Hills in Auburn.', ' The home boasts cathedral ceilings, extensive millwork, crown molding, gleaming hardwoods, chair rails and shadow boxing.', 'Enter the main foyer to a formal entrance with lovely dining and living areas.', ' The kitchen features maple cabinets, stainless appliances, tile counters & granite island eating space.', ' Adjacent to the kitchen is a family room area complete with gas fireplace.', ' This area is sure to be the center of your home activity.', ' Rounding out the main floor is a full-size bedroom and bathroom, and separate laundry room.', ' Lovely volute stairway curves to top floor master suite, complete with master bath.', ' Master bath has skylight, dual sinks, 2 separate walk-in closets.', ' Additionally, there are 3 good sized rooms with another full sized bathroom to round out the top floor.', ' The exterior of the house is a beautiful fenced back yard with an extended patio.', ' Easy maintenance on the yard along with large garage make this home a must see!', 'Property Features:', 'Home is conveniently located only minutes to schools and amenities and easy access to the HWY.', ' It will be available after August 8th for move in.', "Lease Terms: \xa0 Minimum 1 year lease, First month's rent + Security deposit equal to 1 month's rent.", ' No Pets Allowed.', 'Tenant Requirements ***1.', ' Combined credit score of 650+2.', ' Good solid rental history with no evictions3.', ' Verified gross income 3X rentIf you fit these requirements, feel free to apply $30 non-refundable application fee per tenant.', ' For viewings contact me via email, text or phone - Christian']
